com.fortify.util.spring.expression

Class WrappedExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortify.util.spring.expression.WrappedExpression
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.expression.Expression
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SimpleExpression, TemplateExpression

    public class WrappedExpression
extends Object
implements org.springframework.expression.Expression

    This is a simple wrapper class for a Spring Expression instance. This class is used as a based class for both SimpleExpression and TemplateExpression.
